      "en": "Perennial grass with long, thin, horizontal rhizomes that quickly penetrate deep into soil. Flat or erect with blue-green, harshly hairy leaves. Forms dense mats; very difficult to remove due to rhizome fragmentation.",
      "fr": "Graminée vivace aux longs rhizomes horizontaux qui pénètrent rapidement dans le sol. Feuilles bleu-vert grossièrement poilues. Forme des tapis denses; très difficile à enlever en raison de la fragmentation des rhizomes."
