      "en": "Small woody dwarf shrub with green, angled twigs and ovate, finely serrate leaves. The pink, urn-shaped flowers bloom in April-May. The blue-black, bloomy berries are delicious and rich in antioxidants. Stains tongue and fingers blue-purple.",
