      "en": "Fast-growing tree to 20 m with grey-green elliptical leaves that are grey-hairy beneath (never sticky). Catkins appear before leaves in February–March. Fixes nitrogen via root nodules. Distinguished from black alder by grey leaf undersides and more pointed leaf base.",
