      "en": "Erect plant 15–80 cm with whorls of narrow leaves and dense panicles of yellow flowers June–September. Strongly honey-sweet scented. Formerly used to curdle milk for cheese-making (contains rennet-like compounds). Dried plants scented like hay. Host plant for butterflies.",
