      "nl": "Immergroene klimplant of bodembedekker. Jonge bladeren drie- tot vijflobbig; volwassen (bloeiende) bladeren ovaal. Klimt via hechtwortelachtige haartjes. Bloeit september–november. Bessen blauw-zwart, giftig. Enige houtige klimplant inheems in België. Cruciale herfstbloeier voor late insecten.",
      "en": "Evergreen climbing plant or groundcover. Young leaves three- to five-lobed; adult (flowering) leaves oval. Climbs via root-like adhesive hairs. Flowers September–November. Berries blue-black, poisonous. Only woody climber native to Belgium. Crucial autumn bloomer for late insects.",
